          <div class="hidden md:flex md:w-1/2 md:flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <div class="flex-1 flex gap-4 pl-14 md:pl-0">
            <div class="absolute left-0 md:left-1/2 w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-primary bg-white flex items-center justify-center -translate-x-1/2 md:translate-x-0 md:ml-[-20px] flex-shrink-0 z-10 shadow-sm" aria-hidden="true">
              <span class="text-base">💡</span>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-7 bg-white border-2 border-primary/20 flex-1 transition-transform transition-shadow duration-300 ease-out hover:scale-[1.02] hover:shadow-xl">
              <h3 class="text-primary-text font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">What I bring to the table</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-primary-text mt-0.5 font-medium">•</span><span><strong>A Human-Centered Approach:</strong> I bridge the gap between business objectives and user empathy.</span></li>
                <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-primary-text mt-0.5 font-medium">•</span><span><strong>Visual Clarity:</strong> I specialize in creating clean, modern interfaces that prioritize usability without sacrificing aesthetics.</span></li>
                <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-primary-text mt-0.5 font-medium">•</span><span><strong>Enterprise Literacy:</strong> My background at a major financial institution means I am comfortable with complexity, scale, and cross-functional collaboration.</span></li>
